name: Name/Band Bracelet
description:
the Name/Band bracelet is a personalized bracelet. You pick the color and what you want it to say. The maxim is 14 characters. No profanity allowed. email me with your name, your two colors( base color& letter color) and what you want it to say. These do take a little longer than the others.
The band Bracelet is a bracelet with your bands name on it. Wear your favorite bands name on your wrist personalized by you:)
